    API Endpoints Reference
Authentication

POST /api/auth/register - Register new user
POST /api/auth/login - User login
GET /api/auth/me - Get current user (requires JWT)

Games

GET /api/games - List all games
GET /api/games/search?q=query - Search games
GET /api/games/{id} - Get single game

Reviews

GET /api/reviews?page=1&per_page=12&sort=newest - List reviews (with filters)
GET /api/reviews/{id} - Get single review
POST /api/reviews - Create review (requires JWT)
PUT /api/reviews/{id} - Update review (requires JWT)
DELETE /api/reviews/{id} - Delete review (requires JWT)

Votes

POST /api/reviews/{id}/vote - Vote on review (requires JWT)

Comments

GET /api/reviews/{id}/comments - Get comments for review
POST /api/reviews/{id}/comments - Add comment (requires JWT)
DELETE /api/comments/{id} - Delete comment (requires JWT)

File Upload

POST /api/upload/cover - Upload game cover (admin/moderator only)

System

GET /api/health - Health check
GET /api/stats/dashboard - Dashboard statistics

